{"tid":1199643,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"去野餐嘅唔該立即Uninstall 淘寶微訊QQ支那寶 乜乜柒柒","createTime":"2019-06-10T14:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:26:14.000Z","uid":11598,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a134761ef291a19c5253f5b21356a9f7f0fb4498","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"我知有啲人口裡說不手機卻很誠實裝咗呢啲支那App<br />\n唔好心存僥倖覺得唔關你事<br />\n呢啲所有App都有後門<br />\n偷偷錄音呢啲講到噚啦<br />\n呢啲App 仲有機會會log低你location, 周圍WIFI 嘅SSID, 周圍藍牙裝置嘅unique id(如果有grant permission)<br />\n琴晚遊行仲見到啲女開個We7出嚟影相 都痴撚線<br />\n<br />\n真係咁鍾意用就野餐完先裝返 咪累街坊 ！"},{"pid":"c52bb5db79ac55183343d336c47215c01609b666","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n去野餐 4G LTE load 空氣請轉用 3G (H+)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1199394/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1199394/</a>"},{"pid":"df524b1f051ee841ff70bdec0a28dcac8e9d61ab","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:23:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1416c0706474352265980eb9592b40aeb44cd496","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d151b38567e690adf23f322903b0f749077e5ac5","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef820206467886665792e029c8051f7a46609b2","tid":1199643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"why no ppl"},{"pid":"f1fa2f16d481fdff3019ba72bc4d4692ee007d42","tid":1199643,"uid":7949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:36:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"218dc93373e683d01d29de55430202453fa4bb49","tid